  <p>Elena said she was "always tired" from having three children, and Diego said he was "a little tired" too. Words like these — feelings, countries, numbers — are exactly what you need to talk about your own life. Let's build up your vocabulary so you can introduce yourself just as confidently as Elena and Diego did.</p>

