  <h2 class="sec-title"><span class="tab-num" style="background:var(--blue)">&#128483;</span>Speaking Practice</h2>
  <p class="section-intro">Jobs and feelings &mdash; two things people ask about every day: <em>"What do you do?" "How are you?"</em> This week you answer with your voice. Voice memo app ready!</p>

  <div class="speak-card">
    <span class="speak-type">Roleplay: jobs</span>
