      <li>Far: <em>"That is my bag. Those are my books."</em></li>
    </ul>
    <p>Say at least eight sentences &mdash; four near, four far.</p>
    <div class="speak-how"><strong>How:</strong> Really point! Your body helps your brain. Record it. <strong>Check the pairs:</strong> <em>this &rarr; these</em> (near), <em>that &rarr; those</em> (far).</div>
  </div>

  <div class="speak-card">
    <span class="speak-type">Sentence challenge</span>
