<!-- 1: CONTEXT -->
<!-- SECTION: Context First: Read Before Any Rule -->
<section id="context" class="c1">
  <h2 class="sec-title"><span class="tab-num">1</span>Context First: Read Before Any Rule</h2>
  <p>Read how Sam, Elena, Diego and Yuki plan their goodbye party, then what happens at the party itself. Just try to understand. We look at the grammar after.</p>

